name: Cozy
string:
We have both
salt and fresh
water fish here.
You can see them
for free, but we
only have Carp
and King Carp
now… I want to
make this
aquarium a lot
bigger…
I know we've
just met, but
since I don't
have time to do
it myself, can
you go fishing
for me? You can
keep the fish in
your rucksack.
When you get the
fish, give it to
me, and I'll put
them in the fish
tank. If you
want to see the
fish, press the
A Button in
front of the
tank. I'm
counting on you!

name: Cozy
string:
Thank you
<player>! I will
take good
care of it.

name: Choco
string:
I love aquariums
very much!! They
are fun!
